-lrb- cnn -rrb- lauren hill , who took her inspirational fight against brain cancer onto the basketball court and into the hearts of many , has died at age 19 .
the indiana woman 's story became known around the world last year when she was able to realize her dream of playing college basketball .
mount st. joseph university in cincinnati successfully petitioned the ncaa to move up the opening game of its schedule to accommodate her desire to play .
hill died early friday .